{"tid":2057682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點解搭親車都聞到臭榴連味","createTime":"2020-06-09T14:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T17:03:46.000Z","uid":45827,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65b696ed2547b821d373be311850afb59719bce1","tid":2057682,"uid":45827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"窮撚搭親車都焗住要聞啲似垃圾味嘅榴連味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入夏天10次有9次都聞到<br />\n隔住口罩都聞到<br />\n真係好似垃圾味 好想嘔 <br />\n坐咩位都仲聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好多地方都禁帶榴連上交通工具<br />\n就算你搵報紙包到幾密都好<br />\n係冇用㗎屌<br />\n啲臭味都係會漏出嚟<br />\n<br />\n想同食榴連嘅人講<br />\n話知你喺屋企食得有幾開心<br />\n可唔可以唔好拎上車<br />\n生化武器嚟㗎<br />\n好臭呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d82c2b2b4db731a2344d90d327f0899596908d","tid":2057682,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"陣味係你自己個口發出黎"},{"pid":"a24425b9459522eb40b399aaabe7ddc470afe261","tid":2057682,"uid":45827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7d82c2b2b4db731a2344d90d327f0899596908d","tid":2057682,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"陣味係你自己個口發出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"係咪你食完喺你個口發出嚟咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4ccf291fe90eca60609fbc48fba3bbe3daef9f","tid":2057682,"uid":249924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係自己隻腳臭"},{"pid":"a2491c87a2b3c307380ee30d6e8738c67b136b1f","tid":2057682,"uid":157182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"無知一問，香港公共交通工具有冇話唔比？有我就可以大大聲話人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23953616d9abdbe18b26a7d7a7dd405967f2f7b","tid":2057682,"uid":45827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2491c87